      <section class="mb-12">
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">E-commerce warehouses and logistics centers across Malaysia experience dramatic demand surges during Chinese New Year, holiday shopping seasons, and online mega-sales (11.11, 12.12). Without strategic carton box inventory planning, warehouses face packing delays, customer dissatisfaction, and lost revenue. Effective seasonal box management ensures readiness for peak demand periods.</p>
