        <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-6">Forecasting Seasonal Carton Box Demand</h2>
        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Historical Data Analysis</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Review previous peak seasons' order volumes. Chinese New Year typically sees 50–100% volume increases. Holiday shopping (November–December) drives sustained high demand. Use historical data to forecast with 15–20% growth margin for business expansion.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Demand by Season in Malaysia</h3>
        <div class="space-y-2 mt-4">
          <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm"><strong>Chinese New Year (Jan–Feb):</strong> +80–100% volume | Gift packaging, festive items</p>
          <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm"><strong>Holiday Shopping (Oct–Dec):</strong> Sustained high demand | Premium packaging for gifts</p>
          <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm"><strong>Raya Season (Mar–Apr):</strong> +40–60% volume | Festive and gift-related</p>
          <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm"><strong>Online Mega-Sales:</strong> 50% spikes on 11.11, 12.12, 9.9</p>
        </div>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Sizing & Product Mix Planning</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Different seasons require different box sizes. Gift sets need larger presentation boxes. Regular products use standard sizes. Plan a 30–40% small box, 40–50% medium, 20–30% large mix for flexibility across peak seasons.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-6">Warehouse Storage & Inventory Management</h2>
        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Efficient Pallet Storage Systems</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Palletize carton boxes in standard 1.2m x 1.0m x 1.5m configurations (1,000–1,500 boxes per pallet). Use vertical shelving to maximize storage in limited warehouse space common in Balakong and Klang Valley facilities.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">FIFO Rotation & Damage Prevention</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Implement First-In-First-Out (FIFO) systems. Moisture and pests can damage stored boxes. Keep warehouses dry with desiccant packs. Inspect boxes monthly for quality degradation during multi-month seasonal storage.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Pre-Season Order Timing</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Order 4–6 weeks before peak season starts. This allows lead-time buffers and prevents last-minute rushes. Quinocycle's minimum RM 1,000 order facilitates multiple seasonal orders within annual budgets.</p>
      </section>

