            <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm mt-3 leading-relaxed">Quinocycle in Balakong specializes in seasonal wholesale orders. Contact us 4–6 weeks before peak season. Fast delivery across Peninsular Malaysia for warehouse distribution centers.</p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12 bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20 rounded-lg p-8">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Prepare Your Warehouse for Peak Season Success</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Strategic seasonal box planning ensures your warehouse never runs short during critical revenue periods. Quinocycle's flexible ordering and competitive wholesale pricing support peak season demands for Malaysian e-commerce and logistics operations.</p>
